  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D Physics Mayhem!</h2><br>Robozarro is a physics-based, 2-D action game, where robots B0-3 and 0-Ramatron embark on an epic quest through the outskirts, underbelly, and rooftops of Mech Angeles, to uncover the mystery surrounding the disappearance of Dr. Zarro.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2D physics mayhem! Robozarro uses a 2D physics engine that brings the game's action to life, creating unpredictable encounters with enemies!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master the \"Grab N Blast\", a physics-manipulation tool that turns enemies and/or the environment into explosive weapons!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Robots love junk! Collect Junk while adventuring through Mech Angeles and trade it in for Health, grenades, or ammo upgrades!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Recover the Robo-Claw, Mega-Charge, and other gadgets that will aid in your journey across Mech Angeles!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gotta go fast! Unlock Time Trials Mode and attempt to beat levels with no checkpoints and/or no damage!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2D Physics Mayhem!</h2><br>Robozarro is a physics-based, 2-D action game, where robots B0-3 and 0-Ramatron embark on an epic quest through the outskirts, underbelly, and rooftops of Mech Angeles, to uncover the mystery surrounding the disappearance of Dr. Zarro.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2D physics mayhem! Robozarro uses a 2D physics engine that brings the game's action to life, creating unpredictable encounters with enemies!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master the \"Grab N Blast\", a physics-manipulation tool that turns enemies and/or the environment into explosive weapons!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Robots love junk! Collect Junk while adventuring through Mech Angeles and trade it in for Health, grenades, or ammo upgrades!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Recover the Robo-Claw, Mega-Charge, and other gadgets that will aid in your journey across Mech Angeles!</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gotta go fast! Unlock Time Trials Mode and attempt to beat levels with no checkpoints and/or no damage!</li></ul>",
